// ====================================================================
// ========================= OperatorRegistry =========================
// ====================================================================
// Frax Finance: https://github.com/FraxFinance

// Primary Author(s)
// Jack Corddry: https://github.com/corddry
// Justin Moore: https://github.com/0xJM

